text: Aribashevo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kudashevsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 273 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 9 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 5 km from Verkhnekudashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Aribashevo
